igure><p>Carthage, a great city located on the North African coast in what is present day Tunisia, was itself practically invulnerable. It had a brilliant harbor, and the Carthaginians constructed the most advanced (and it must be said beautiful) circular harbor in which it protect its Navy. It was a maritime superpower.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcc7b9ef4-6fb1-4b3b-b158-4b679b66ba61_1258x543.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/ATaC2C06AIg6GOKK7MrrlWl9Yc5Jv49ql-dxPF6aLkE=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZjYzdiOWVmNC02ZmIxLTRiM2ItYjE1OC00YjY3OWI2NmJhNjFfMTI1OHg1NDMucG5n 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/lRbCNy8is66Ne7oKZyHG4E9LmzhffvUtX0-V2qHY0Ok=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGY2M3YjllZjQtNmZiMS00YjNiLWIxNTgtNGI2NzliNjZiYTYxXzEyNTh4NTQzLnBuZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Ru6doFK0_ehoHYtc5hvyECpBD6e6GRbWMfhAu-e7SlA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGY2M3YjllZjQtNmZiMS00YjNiLWIxNTgtNGI2NzliNjZiYTYxXzEyNTh4NTQzLnBuZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/6AEanVKWYZlKpY-" alt="CDN media" title="CDN media" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/d37EBj0bm-Vx7AYZUccz-gVAail_EBEZlwK7xo2ARO0=/aHR0cHM6L